  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time voice conversations with hands-free, headphone-free voice interruption",
    "Live2D avatar with expression control driven by LLM output",
    "Fully offline operation — all models run locally on your machine",
    "Cross-platform support for Windows, macOS, and Linux",
    "Modular engine system: swap LLM, ASR, and TTS backends via config file",
    "Desktop pet mode with transparent background and always-on-top window",
    "Visual perception — AI can see your screen or camera feed",
    "MCP (Model Context Protocol) tool integration for extended AI capabilities",
    "Live streaming integration (Bilibili) for AI VTuber broadcasts",
    "Multi-character support with persona prompts and voice cloning"
  ],
